sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Next.js UI
    participant API as FastAPI /v2/compare
    participant CACHE as Comparison Cache
    participant Q as Celery + Redis
    participant W as Worker compare_v2
    participant CMP as RealDiffEngine
    participant V as Weaviate
    participant L as Ollama

    U->>FE: Select doc1/doc2 and compare
    FE->>API: POST /v2/compare
    API->>CACHE: lookup(doc1, doc2)

    alt Cache hit
        API-->>FE: 202 finished + cacheHit + result
    else Cache miss
        API->>Q: send_task(compare_v2)
        API-->>FE: 202 queued + jobId
        loop Until terminal state
            FE->>API: GET /v2/compare/response/{jobId}
            API->>Q: AsyncResult(jobId)
            API-->>FE: queued | running | finished | failed
        end
        Q->>W: Deliver compare task
        W->>CMP: compare(doc1, doc2)
        CMP->>V: fetch + semantic/hybrid matching
        CMP->>L: summarize/action/follow-up generation
        W->>CACHE: save comparison result
        W-->>Q: SUCCESS with result payload
    end
